# phaze-he8m: keep ./certs/ in the repo so a git clone materializes it owned by
# the cloning operator (uid 1000), NOT auto-created root:root by rootful dockerd.
# The api service bind-mounts ./certs:/certs:rw and the uid-1000 cert bootstrap
# writes phaze-ca.crt here on first start; a root-owned dir crashes it with
# PermissionError before uvicorn binds.
